@Vladimir_4757 Oh, and "Congress shall make no law respecting an establishment of religion," is from the 1st Amendment not the Constitution itself. 

And show me where it says religious symbols are illegal? Last I checked our money had God in we Trust inscripted on it and the Ten Commandments are frequently displayed in courthouses. 

